Definition: Represents virtual conference call details. Based on https://jira.hl7.org/browse/FHIR-33341. Once an official implementation for video meeting details is added to the FHIR standard and can be backported to R4, this extension will be replaced
Unique id for the element within a resource (for internal references). This may be any string value that does not contain spaces.
An Extension
Slicing Description: Extensions are always sliced by (at least) url
Constraint(s):
ele-1:All FHIR elements must have a @value or children {hasValue() or (children().count() > id.count())}
ext-1:Must have either extensions or value[x], not both {extension.exists() != value.exists()}
